{"tid":1803386,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"同屬22歲 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-30T07:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:18:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4434336939efb0c8928fd8a8979d0713ebf9440","tid":1803386,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191230/20833700/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191230%2F20833700%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkST1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=a352db72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191230%2F20833700%2F&h=1fbacbeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191230/20833700/</a><br />\n<br />\n同屬22歲 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191230/large/1577598778_2c6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191230%2Flarge%2F1577598778_2c6a.jpg&h=cd2165b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名22歲女子，日前在中區地利根德里世紀大廈墮樓身亡，警方稱事件「無可疑」，完。<br />\n<br />\n死者是立法會議員張華峰幼女，「好乖好善良」，近兩年患躁鬱症由英回港就醫，每次出入豪宅都有人陪同。對愛女最終自殺，張表示「唔知點解會咁」。<br />\n<br />\n以下只是白描：──67歲的張華峰體重約250磅，政界「肥老闆」，是立會金融服務界議員、監警會副主席，一向撐警撐政府，曾指警暴進行時可不必展示編號以免被起底，執法便無後顧之憂。令示威者不寒而慄的新屋嶺扣留中心，投訴者披露酷刑、輪姦、阻見律師、暴虐至失去意識事件，曾否出人命是個謎。張視察後卻表示，裏面情況「都幾好，地方幾乾淨，仲有冷氣添。」<br />\n<br />\n在將軍澳停車場詭異被墮樓重傷不治的科大學生周梓樂，終年22歲。民主派於立會開始時站立默哀，明明已到場的張離席出去，建制派在默哀後才進場──亡女同屬22歲，若有默哀張會離席嗎？你的子女是人，人家的子女不是寶貴的生命？還有數千被上吊被跳樓被跳海的亡魂呢？<br />\n<br />\n白描中忍住不提「報應」二字，但怎麼逃得掉？據知，有些做過傷天害理之事的黑警，種因得果，報在無辜子女身上──不過當局怕「士氣」、「軍心」受挫，密封消息，但風聲隨天意洩漏。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"2d9d483e30a1225fb25d6292d1c5e85a4f894496","tid":1803386,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:17:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和你SHOP</span><br />\n12月31日 星期二<br />\n時間 : 1800-2100<br />\n地點 : 時代廣場, 圓方, 海港城<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkST1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=0824662d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Suck The Eve</span><br />\n12月31日 星期二<br />\n時間 :  22:00<br />\n地點 : 時代廣場, 圓方, 海港城<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkST1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=0824662d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書"},{"pid":"7987fd71920408c88f880ab984d9095e49925e7e","tid":1803386,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkST1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=281bc39b\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html<